    <!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
    <string name="privacy_policy_content">
        We value your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how FinLog collects, uses, and protects your personal information.\n\n
        **1. Data Collection**\n
        We collect information such as financial records, card details, and account balances to provide our services. This data is stored locally on your device.\n\n
        **2. Data Usage**\n
        Your data is used solely to manage your financial records within the app. We do not share your information with third parties.\n\n
        **3. Data Security**\n
        We use secure methods to store your data locally. However, you are responsible for securing your device.\n\n
        **4. Changes to This Policy**\n
        We may update this policy from time to time. Please review it periodically.\n\n
        If you have any questions, please contact us at support@finlogapp.com.
    </string>

    <!-- Support Content -->
    <string name="support_content">
        We’re here to help you with FinLog!\n\n
        **Contact Us**\n
        Email: support@finlogapp.com\n\n
        **Frequently Asked Questions**\n
        - **How do I add a new record?**\n
          Go to the Records tab and click the "+" button to add a new record.\n
        - **How do I back up my data?**\n
          Go to the Menu tab and select "Create Backup" to save your data.\n
        - **How do I restore my data?**\n
          Go to the Menu tab and select "Restore Backup" to recover your data.\n\n
        For more help, please email us, and we’ll get back to you as soon as possible!
    </string>
